Doc: Defines a condition when an event applies.

Source.Contents:
/#
 Defines a condition when an event applies.
 #/
enum FpML5.confirmation.ConditionEnum {
    # The event rate must be greater than or equal to the specified trigger rate.
    AtOrAbove 
    # The event rate must be less than or equal to the specified trigger rate.
    AtOrBelow 
    # The event rate must be greater than the specified trigger rate.
    Above 
    # The event rate must be less than the specified trigger rate.
    Below 

}

AtOrAbove.Doc: The event rate must be greater than or equal to the specified trigger rate.
AtOrAbove.Name: AtOrAbove

AtOrBelow.Doc: The event rate must be less than or equal to the specified trigger rate.
AtOrBelow.Name: AtOrBelow

Above.Doc: The event rate must be greater than the specified trigger rate.
Above.Name: Above

Below.Doc: The event rate must be less than the specified trigger rate.
Below.Name: Below
